<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index up 3.15 Points </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, October 20 (Xinhua) - The general price index at
Tehran Stock Exchange closed Tuesday at 1,565.9 points, up by
3.15 points compared to that on Monday.
</P>
<P>
A total of 1,287,167 shares exchanged hands in 140 turns and
the turnover stood at 3.75 billion rials (682,000 U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The shares of 39 companies made gains while those of 13 others
declined. 
</P>
</TEXT>
