<HEADLINE> Kuwait Stock Exchange Index Closes Higher </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUWAIT CITY, October 21 (Xinhua) -- Kuwait Stock Exchange
index closed at 2,007.8 Wednesday, up 1.4 points.
</P>
