technology," she said, pointing to the fact that diploma engineers
are directly involved in the implementation process of development
programs, and that the world, which is at the threshold of the
21st century, would witness culmination of scientific and
technological developments.
</P>
<P>
Scientist, technologists and engineers must take the
initiatives to this end and assured them of providing adequate
government support to their efforts, she stressed.
</P>
<P>
"Without wasting time, we must begin to act now to prepare
ourselves for the new century," she vowed, saying that the
posterity must be enabled to make South Asia prosperous and meet
challenges of time.
</P>
