<HEADLINE> Albanian Police Seize 2.8 Kg of Cocaine </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Albanian Police felt suspicious of the two men when they
arrived at Tirana Rinas Airport.
</P>
<P>
Police searched them after a junior official from the Albanian
intelligence bureau showed up to greet them. Two kilograms of
cocaine were found tied around the waists of the Italian and the
