<HEADLINE> Highlights of Beijing-based Newspapers </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, October 21 (Xinhua) -- Highlights of today's major
Beijing-based newspapers:
</P>
<P>
 "People's Daily"
</P>
<P>
-- Chinese President Jiang Zemin met with visiting Vietnamese
Prime Minister Phan Van Khai yesterday afternoon in Beijing. Jiang
said China and Vietnam should work hard on their modernization
drives to contribute to regional peace, stability and development,
</P>
<P>
