<TEXT>
<P>
HAIKOU, October 21 (Xinhua) -- A Sino-Japanese motorcycle joint
venture went into production on Monday in the Guilinyang Economic
Development Zone in the island province of Hainan.
</P>
<P>
The Hainan Sundiro-Kawasaki Engine Co. Ltd. involves a cost of
about 50 million U.S. dollars and is equipped with seven advanced
processing lines and an engine production line.
</P>
<P>
