C. Itoh &AMP; Co. Ltd. and Hainan's Xindazhou Motorcycle Co. Ltd., is
the third Sino-Japanese cooperative project in Hainan. With assets
of over two billion yuan, Xindazhou Motorcycle is listed on the
stock exchange in China. 
