to be Tyson's manager.
</P>
<P>
"I'll be the closest guy to him, making all the
decisions,"Johnson said.
</P>
<P>
But sources close to Tyson said fight manager Shelly Finkel
will continue his job as Tyson's main adviser.
</P>
<P>
